data.description: This home is updated to pinterest perfection top to bottom while maintaining original charm & character! Classic arch ways greet you as you enter both the living & dining rooms and crown molding is featured throughout! The first floor boasts tall ceilings, large windows letting in lots of natural light, large room sizes, and beautiful warm toned LVP flooring throughout.  The dining area features an adorable built in hutch & is open to the kitchen making it perfect for entertaining family & friends! The Joanna Gaines approved kitchen includes subway tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances & farmhouse inspired lighting. Step out of the kitchen & onto the covered porch & enjoy your tabletop flat, fenced in backyard! Upstairs you will find 3 spacious bedrooms & an updated full bathroom- shower & tub replaced in 2023! The basement was just recently finished and is another great living space! Furnace and AC replaced in 2021! Conveniently located, only minutes to Pittsburgh!
